title: Kamala Keeps Talking
description: Fellas laugh about Kamala's speaking struggles before discussing Democrat's new plan to raise taxes on small businesses during a recession. Northern Virginia Congressional candidate, Hung Cao, and Common Sense Leadership Fund Executive Director, Kevin McLaughlin, join the progrum.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Kevin McLaughlin, Hung Cao, Comfortably Smug, John Ashbrook, Josh Holmes)
